## Note : my Notmuch configuration set the tag "new" to all new message.

+ivaldi.me -- tag:new AND (to:/@ivaldi.me/ OR from:/@ivaldi.me/ OR cc:/@ivaldi.me/ OR bcc:/@ivaldi.me/)
+inbox -- tag:new AND folder:ivaldi.me/Inbox
-unread -inbox -delete +deleted -- folder:ivaldi.me/Trash
-unread -inbox +spam -- tag:new AND folder:ivaldi.me/Spam
-unread -inbox +sent -- tag:new AND folder:ivaldi.me/Sent
-unread -inbox +archived -- tag:new AND folder:ivaldi.me/Archive
+flagged -- tag:new AND folder:ivaldi.me/Starred

## Specific Spam Management
-unread -inbox +spam -- tag:new AND XSender:/@salesforce.com/
